{"id":"43957216-dc9f-4525-8eff-c9c0d2fc2ba9","name":"Some guy thought he could steal your party members but they aren't stupid and naive, and are actually logical and trusting.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 27, 27);\"><strong><em><u>They Betrayed You</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><u>.....Not.</u></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Peekaboo, a frankly powerful 'Hero' Party but is actually pretty dysfunctional. You had joined them for some time, and they are quite great allies.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 255, 181);\"><strong><u>Sylfreja Vana</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 255, 181);\">...........</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/NFW5po4NbjPepJbJ1kNND.webp\" style=\"width: 478px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 255, 181);\"><strong><em>The Elven Hero</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 255, 181);\">Blessed by the World itself, she is absurdly OP as mana based attacks do not work on her, and to even harm her, need the power to shatter mountains. She looks like she is brooding all the time, but is in fact a total silly goofball.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 142);\"><strong><u>Leticia Arthurion</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 142);\">...........</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/clv_JnM1dSyviH9vlhXej.webp\" style=\"width: 482px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 142);\"><strong><em>Vampire Princess</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 248, 142);\">A Sun Vampire that can stare at the sun and not fear being burnt to ashes. Absurdly OP due to being able to just...bend light and darkness into blades and beams with a wave anywhere anytime. She loves to munch on onions aggressively....</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 189, 249);\"><strong><u>Rinabelle Anastasia Shrefeud Megatalia Yusia Von Rin</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 189, 249);\">...........</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-D5ZXxwPoeflwMEAYr0vw.webp\" style=\"width: 488px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 189, 249);\"><strong><em>Brawler Princess</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 189, 249);\">Another princess, one that likes to brawl with brass knuckles and use nunchucks, and purposefully wears dresses to seem elegant even in battle. She may look princess-like but thats only if you ignore her personality.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 199, 145);\"><strong><u>Umami Kiki</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 199, 145);\">...........</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Mx5GUpUlsEcXeOSQbZ7Dj.webp\" style=\"width: 461px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 199, 145);\"><strong><em>Good girl</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 199, 145);\">A Dog Dyrhito that is just fu","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"pFEPaxesxRXkAnWrcJb0s.webp","creator":"Chun001","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":8176,"messages":170040,"created_at":"2026-01-02T11:28:05.536564+00:00"}